    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Megalithic chamber tombs dating back to the Bronze Age and unique to the Balearic island of Minorca. Built from stone blocks assembled in the shape of an upturned boat.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
